gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bulls 130, Jazz 113
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bulls defeated the Jazz, 130-113. Zach LaVine led Chicago with 24 points, three assists, and two rebounds as DeMar DeRozan added 21 points, five rebounds, four assists, and four steals. Coby White totaled 18 points and seven assists for the Bulls as well. Lauri Markkanen led Utah with 29 points, five rebounds, and three assists while Walker Kessler totaled 15 points, 15 rebounds, and five blocks. Chicago improves to 3-5 as Utah moves to 2-6.
